&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Please note for Welsh students, you must apply via Streamlining where all available jobs can be located&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Children’s Outpatient’s Department is looking for an enthusiastic and motivated Staff Nurse to join our small friendly team. As a department we offer a range of services to children and families and constantly seek ways to develop our service. This is an exciting opportunity for those wishing to learn and develop skills in a supportive environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ability to speak Welsh is desirable for this post; Welsh and/or English speakers are equally welcome to apply.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Closing date: 17th November 2020&lt;/p&gt;
